## Next Steps

After deployment to Vercel:
1. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard for this project
2. Navigate to Project Settings → Analytics → Enable
3. Once enabled, the `/_vercel/insights/view` endpoint will be available
4. View analytics data in the Vercel dashboard under the Analytics tab

## Technical Notes

- The Analytics component is lightweight and won't impact application performance
- It automatically tracks page views and visitor metrics
- Route changes are automatically detected through react-router-dom integration
